  "commit_message": "fix(install): keep format-transformed rules tracked + in sync (closes #1662) (#1665)\n\n* fix(install): keep format-transformed rules tracked + in sync (closes #1662)\n\nFormat-transforming instruction targets (.claude/rules, .cursor/rules,\n.windsurf/rules) are never byte-identical to their source, so the source-based\nadopt in integrate_instructions_for_target() always missed: an existing rule was\ntreated as a user-authored collision and skipped, never (re)written, and never\nrecorded in local_deploy",
